TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT Customer_Event_Group, Account_name, Country_Code FROM ( SELECT Customer_Event_Group, Account_name, Country_Code ,rank() over (partition by Account_Name, Country_Code ORDER BY IIF(Customer_Event_Group=Account_name,0,1),IIF(CHARINDEX('Oth',Customer_Event_Group)=0,0,1),Customer_Event_Group) Rnk FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT LTRIM(RTRIM(A.Customer_Event_Group)) Customer_Event_Group, LTRIM(RTRIM(B.Account_name)) Account_name, B.Country_Code FROM dbo.CUSTOMER_EVENT_GROUP A WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN dbo.customer_vw B WITH (NOLOCK) ON A.Customer_Event_Group_ID=B.Customer_Event_Group_ID WHERE B.Account_name is not NULL ) A ) A WHERE Rnk=1
